You shall see them again no more forever.

19:19.786 --> 19:21.127
I got some people in here tonight.

19:24.951 --> 19:26.813
Fear not.

19:26.833 --> 19:28.054
Stand still.

19:29.075 --> 19:30.857
Oh my God, it's spoken unto you.

19:30.897 --> 19:31.658
Come on, somebody.

19:32.719 --> 19:33.720
Fear not.

19:34.481 --> 19:35.942
I don't care about the attacks.

19:36.223 --> 19:37.624
I don't care what the enemy said.

19:38.125 --> 19:39.506
Fear not.

19:39.842 --> 19:43.608
Stand still, see the salvation of the Lord.

19:43.888 --> 19:46.612
See God's deliverance on your behalf, come on.

19:46.632 --> 19:50.998
Because what you see today, you ain't gonna ever see no more.

20:00.973 --> 20:02.716
The Lord shall fight for you.

20:04.518 --> 20:07.122
See, sometimes you ain't gotta do nothing.

20:07.522 --> 20:09.064
Let the talkers talk.

20:09.445 --> 20:13.129
Let all the people come on.

20:13.149 --> 20:13.830
Let them talk.

20:13.910 --> 20:15.312
Let them do the day thing.

20:16.934 --> 20:18.997
Let the Lord fight for you.

20:19.017 --> 20:24.064
I don't care what it is.

20:24.104 --> 20:26.847
Let God fight for you.

20:27.969 --> 20:34.137
See, we believers and we try to fight everything in our own might, in our own strength, in our own ability.

20:34.177 --> 20:35.058
Come on, somebody.

20:35.426 --> 20:37.889
God is saying, let me fight for you.

20:37.929 --> 20:41.593
Let me fight this battle for you, glory to God.

20:43.615 --> 20:44.857
The Lord's your fight for you.

20:44.877 --> 20:48.241
And you shall hold your peace.

20:50.984 --> 20:52.065
That's a word right there.

20:52.085 --> 20:52.806
Come on, somebody.

20:54.968 --> 20:56.310
I ain't got a fight in this thing.

20:58.072 --> 21:03.698
I can operate in the peace of God when the storms of life are raging against me.

21:04.386 --> 21:06.330
I can operate in the peace of God.

21:07.712 --> 21:15.106
When I'm catching it on my job, catching it on my marriage, catching it in my eye can operate in the peace of God.

21:15.166 --> 21:15.988
Come on, somebody.

21:19.114 --> 21:23.001
And the Lord said unto Moses, wherefore Christ thou unto me?

21:23.462 --> 21:27.730
Speak unto the children of Israel that they go forward.

21:28.802 --> 21:32.148
It is not time for you to retreat in your relationship with God.

21:32.549 --> 21:38.961
It's not time for you to throw in the tower and say this Christian stuff don't work or this relationship with God stuff don't work.

21:39.282 --> 21:42.107
No, God is telling us to move forward.

21:44.431 --> 21:46.455
We got to go forward in God.

21:46.715 --> 21:48.799
Go forward in our relationship with God.

21:49.060 --> 21:50.763
That means you need to pray again.

